body_html:
Good point on the build_all not passing through arguments, I should look at that.

Are you seeing this when you build the Simple example at https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/tree/master/tensorflow/contrib/ios_examples/simple ? The reason I'm asking is that the size of the libs on disk and the final size they contribute to an executable can be pretty different, so I want to check how you're building your final binary.
